headline.main: Paid Notice: Memorials  SCHWEDE, WILLIAM AND ROBERT

snippet: SCHWEDE--William and Robert. We shared the same birthday, all three of us. Miss you William, and Robert, my identical twin, more and more each day. Your loving brother always, Raymond 1/3
